{"tid":1377784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要記住，前線唔係Condom，不分化不割蓆","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:32:45.000Z","uid":148783,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e2aca44497670bf51e34cc594ae96e577e14e2","tid":1377784,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求入面，我地要求釋放被捕義士<br />\n就算有前線比黑警拘捕左都好，請唔好擔心<br />\n繼續我無野講，搵律師<br />\n政府一日唔回應五大訴求，抗爭一日唔會完<br />\n你地拉我地前線，只會激發更多既前線<br />\n你地以為拉左義士我地就會驚？<br />\n我地只會堅持到底，無一個義士係condom<br />\n我地唔會放棄抗爭，我地唔會放棄比人拉左既義士<br />\n呢個係我地既立場，係底線<br />\n所以前線唔洗擔心，我地係唔會放棄任何一個人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直至政府回應五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直至一日我地可以除底口罩面罩攬住一齊喊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即回應五大訴求，釋放所有被捕人士</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef249bcfa0a82b4d34f865eb7947a3256c962bc0","tid":1377784,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b83095d0beebcd8a014d94b52a6eadc4bffb0775","tid":1377784,"uid":148783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8646ec016c23e1893b46e5181f3658bd79551dee","tid":1377784,"uid":38237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n要光復香港，大家一齊手動罷工啦！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n打爆啲交通燈會唔會易過全民死火燈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1377458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1377458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa2d3251c40c7accab